snippet.title: Slapshot: Rebound - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Welcome to SLAPSHOT Rebound.

ALPHA SIGNUP: https://slapshot.gg

Exactly one year after releasing the first Slapshot game we are happy to present you with the gameplay teaser of SLAPSHOT Rebound.

SLAPSHOT Rebound is a competitive yet lighthearted hockey video game where you battle your opponents on the ice and try to score the puck more than them within the five minute window.

The game is set to release into Early Access in the summer of 2020.

Join us on Discord for the latest news https://discord.gg/slapshot
For more, follow our Twitter https://twitter.com/slapshotgg
